



Govr
[Fort Loudoun] June 11th [1757]



Send to him the proceedings of the Enquiry Court upon Lt Campbell.1
DittoInstructns to the Offrs of Out Posts.
Not to provide any Indians with Horses but in extraordinary Cases nor to hold any conferences & treatys with them or to make them any Promisesnor give them liquor.2
Mr KingDitto3
Tell him to take up all the Horses brot by the Indians from the Indians & to take great pains in having them delivd to their proper owners.
